from a poor kid from Gary.

1055
01:27:34.082 --> 01:27:35.083
Who would have thought?

1056
01:27:36.126 --> 01:27:38.837
Me. I thought.

1057
01:27:44.259 --> 01:27:45.343
Come here.

1058
01:27:46.803 --> 01:27:48.638
Joseph. I know you want something.

1059
01:27:53.560 --> 01:27:54.770
Michael...

1060
01:27:56.772 --> 01:27:58.982
I'm gonna need you to tour
with your brothers.

1061
01:28:00.567 --> 01:28:03.069
Now. I let you do that album 
by yourself.

1062
01:28:04.237 --> 01:28:05.989
I'm gonna need you to do this for me.

1063
01:28:07.866 --> 01:28:08.950
For your family.

1064
01:28:10.535 --> 01:28:12.704
I'm not a child anymore. Joseph.

1065
01:28:13.789 --> 01:28:15.499
And you're not my manager.
-Here we go.

1066
01:28:15.582 --> 01:28:17.709
I have to start living my own life.

1067
01:28:19.711 --> 01:28:20.921
On my own.

1068
01:28:21.963 --> 01:28:23.590
Just like everyone else.

1069
01:28:23.673 --> 01:28:25.425
You ain't like everyone else.

1070
01:28:28.428 --> 01:28:31.306
So. you're trying to tell me
you want to be treated like an adult?

1071
01:28:32.474 --> 01:28:33.892
All right.

1072
01:28:33.975 --> 01:28:37.646
You want to see what the world is like

1073
01:28:38.855 --> 01:28:40.816
without a family that protects you.

1074
01:28:42.234 --> 01:28:44.653
Without a family that...

1075
01:28:45.654 --> 01:28:46.738
understands you.

1076
01:28:47.823 --> 01:28:51.243
Nobody else will understand you
outside this place.

1077
01:28:51.326 --> 01:28:54.204
There you'll be with
all the money in the world.

1078
01:28:54.287 --> 01:28:56.206
surrounded by people who'll say "yes"

1079
01:28:57.082 --> 01:28:59.501
to everything.

1080
01:29:00.794 --> 01:29:02.003
Is that what you want?

1081
01:29:06.758 --> 01:29:08.093
What kind of sense that make?

1082
01:29:16.518 --> 01:29:17.519
I'm gonna...

1083
01:29:18.228 --> 01:29:19.521
call Don King

1084
01:29:20.230 --> 01:29:22.065
and tell him you're doing a tour.

1085
01:29:24.693 --> 01:29:26.653
I know you don't want to let
your family down.

1086
01:30:06.902 --> 01:30:08.820
Cut! Cut! Cut! Cut!

1087
01:30:11.781 --> 01:30:14.117
All right. here's what I need.
I'm thinking...

1088
01:30:15.744 --> 01:30:18.371
I move the camera in while 
you're up here.

1089
01:30:18.455 --> 01:30:21.291
I need to get a close up
of you at the top.

1090
01:30:21.374 --> 01:30:23.543
so just feel the camera 
as you come down.

1091
01:30:23.627 --> 01:30:25.295
Okay.
-Okay. great. All right.

1092
01:30:25.378 --> 01:30:27.631
Okay. everybody.

1093
01:30:27.714 --> 01:30:31.426
Here we go. What is this?
What do we got? Take six?

1094
01:30:31.509 --> 01:30:32.886
Lucky six. Lucky six.

1095
01:30:32.969 --> 01:30:34.596
Here we go. Energy. everybody!

1096
01:30:34.679 --> 01:30:37.182
You love The Jacksons.
You love The Jacksons.

1097
01:30:37.265 --> 01:30:39.100
You love Pepsi. Let's go!

1098
01:30:40.310 --> 01:30:41.895
A marker!

1099
01:30:41.978 --> 01:30:44.022
B mark!

1100
01:30:44.105 --> 01:30:45.190
C mark.

1101
01:30:45.273 --> 01:30:46.900
And playback.

1102
01:31:15.053 --> 01:31:16.179
Cut it.

1103
01:31:20.308 --> 01:31:21.393
Michael!

1104
01:31:23.061 --> 01:31:24.229
What happened?

1105
01:31:25.397 --> 01:31:27.065
Mike. are you okay?
-Back up!

1106
01:31:27.148 --> 01:31:29.526
Bill. get him out of here!
-Here. Michael!

1107
01:31:30.360 --> 01:31:31.319
Over here. Joker. Come here.

1108
01:31:31.403 --> 01:31:33.321
Hey. you're gonna be okay. okay?
You're gonna be okay.

1109
01:31:33.405 --> 01:31:34.781
Come on. Mike. Clear a path!

1110
01:31:38.243 --> 01:31:40.286
Out of my way!
Michael. I'm coming!

1111
01:31:41.371 --> 01:31:43.665
Get back! Get out of my way! 
Clear a path!

1112
01:31:43.748 --> 01:31:45.750
Get back! Get back!

1113
01:31:46.668 --> 01:31:49.879
Clear a path! Move! Move. please!

1114
01:31:49.963 --> 01:31:51.256
Michael!

1115
01:31:52.674 --> 01:31:53.883
Excuse me!

1116
01:32:24.372 --> 01:32:26.124
Kate. Kate. come on.

1117
01:32:28.460 --> 01:32:30.378
Hey. I need to talk to you.
-Sir.

1118
01:32:30.462 --> 01:32:32.088
I'm his father. Joseph Jackson.

1119
01:32:32.172 --> 01:32:33.673
This is his mother. Katherine.

1120
01:32:33.757 --> 01:32:35.550
Hi. It's good to meet you.
-Very nice to meet you.

1121
01:32:35.633 --> 01:32:36.885
Thank you.

1122
01:32:36.968 --> 01:32:39.471
Well. your son is in stable condition.

1123
01:32:39.554 --> 01:32:40.930
All right.
-All right?

1124
01:32:41.014 --> 01:32:43.308
And. uh. we're trying to bring
his heart rate down.

1125
01:32:43.391 --> 01:32:44.768
but he's in a lot of pain.

1126
01:32:46.186 --> 01:32:47.604
Okay. When will he recover?

1127
01:32:47.687 --> 01:32:48.813
It's too soon to tell.

1128
01:32:49.731 --> 01:32:51.691
It's gonna be a long road. 
all right?

1129
01:32:51.775 --> 01:32:54.778
He has third-degree burns
and substantial nerve damage.

1130
01:32:56.905 --> 01:32:57.906
Okay.

1131
01:32:58.698 --> 01:33:01.785
Do you think he'll ever be able
to perform again?

1132
01:33:01.868 --> 01:33:02.786
Ever?

1133
01:33:03.369 --> 01:33:04.746
Joseph.

1134
01:33:08.208 --> 01:33:11.419
Mr. Jackson. your son almost died.

1135
01:33:11.503 --> 01:33:12.837
I know that.

1136
01:33:12.921 --> 01:33:14.839
Well. if that fire had caught 
his clothes.

1137
01:33:14.923 --> 01:33:17.801
or burned over to his face
and eyes. he wouldn't be here.

1138
01:33:17.884 --> 01:33:19.094
I know my boy.

1139
01:33:19.928 --> 01:33:23.765
And the only thing that's gonna heal 
him is by getting back on that stage.

1140
01:33:24.808 --> 01:33:26.434
That's where he lives.

1141
01:33:26.518 --> 01:33:28.103
I understand that. sir.

1142
01:33:28.186 --> 01:33:29.562
But it's gonna be a while.
-Do you? All right.

1143
01:33:29.646 --> 01:33:31.648
Yes. I do. But. Mr. Jackson...

1144
01:33:32.524 --> 01:33:35.026
he's gonna need your support 
to get there.

1145
01:33:35.110 --> 01:33:36.528
I'm sorry.

1146
01:33:43.159 --> 01:33:44.953
It's unlikely
that will grow back.

1147
01:33:45.954 --> 01:33:49.040
You'll need surgery
to laser the scar tissue

1148
01:33:49.124 --> 01:33:51.751
and stretch part of the scalp
over the burn.

1149
01:33:52.836 --> 01:33:56.089
All right? We'll insert an implant
to protect the scalp.

1150
01:33:56.172 --> 01:33:58.007
Will I have to wear a wig?

1151
01:33:58.091 --> 01:33:59.592
Well. right there on top.

1152
01:34:02.011 --> 01:34:04.430
What kind of wig? Like. a full wig?

1153
01:34:04.514 --> 01:34:05.765
Hard to say.

1154
01:34:05.849 --> 01:34:08.101
There are prosthetic hair weaves
we can try.

1155
01:34:08.184 --> 01:34:11.354
but we won't know until we see
how the surgery goes next week.

1156
01:34:12.188 --> 01:34:14.607
Michael! Michael! Michael!

1157
01:34:19.529 --> 01:34:20.738
You'll. um...

1158
01:34:21.698 --> 01:34:23.867
You'll have to stay
on the Demerol for a while.

1159
01:34:23.950 --> 01:34:25.702
I don't want to take medication.

1160
01:34:26.411 --> 01:34:29.289
I have to be honest. Mr. Jackson.
you're gonna need them.

1161
01:34:30.123 --> 01:34:32.375
We have to replace
the implant periodically.

1162
01:34:32.458 --> 01:34:34.502
The nerves are exposed up there.

1163
01:34:34.586 --> 01:34:36.296
You'll be in a lot of pain.

1164
01:34:39.174 --> 01:34:41.801
I'll let you rest. 
but I'll be back later.

1165
01:34:45.221 --> 01:34:47.807
Michael! Michael! Michael!

1166
01:34:47.891 --> 01:34:50.143
We'll stay here
'till you're better. Michael.

1167
01:34:50.226 --> 01:34:51.603
You see the number of people

1168
01:34:51.686 --> 01:34:53.897
who have already gathered
outside the hospital.

1169
01:34:53.980 --> 01:34:55.607
If that isn't a testament

1170
01:34:55.690 --> 01:34:58.276
to the star power of Michael Jackson.
I don't know what is.

1171
01:34:58.359 --> 01:35:00.653
The fans say they won't go back
until Michael Jackson's all right.

1172
01:35:03.573 --> 01:35:04.991
All right.

1173
01:35:05.074 --> 01:35:06.492
All right. Joker.

1174
01:35:07.118 --> 01:35:08.536
Got all your favorites.

1175
01:35:08.620 --> 01:35:10.705
Golden Temple. they send their love.

1176
01:35:10.788 --> 01:35:12.624
Got some Mexican.
-Golden Temple's your favorite. Michael.

1177
01:35:12.707 --> 01:35:13.917
Chinese. Some fried chicken.

1178
01:35:14.000 --> 01:35:15.877
Even got these
little red candies you like.

1179
01:35:17.420 --> 01:35:20.965
Thanks. Bill. 
You can just leave it there.

1180
01:35:21.049 --> 01:35:22.258
I'm not hungry.

1181
01:35:23.134 --> 01:35:24.344
Okay.

1182
01:35:28.348 --> 01:35:29.766
I'll leave you all to it.

1183
01:35:29.849 --> 01:35:32.477
Okay. Thank you. Bill.

1184
01:36:00.421 --> 01:36:01.839
I'm sorry. Michael.

1185
01:36:06.177 --> 01:36:07.804
I should have protected you.

1186
01:36:09.639 --> 01:36:13.142
Mother. I don't want
to discuss this right now.

1187
01:36:14.394 --> 01:36:15.478
Okay.

1188
01:36:22.235 --> 01:36:23.736
No one can stop Joseph.

1189
01:36:27.407 --> 01:36:28.491
Nobody.

1190
01:36:37.208 --> 01:36:39.752
You just know that.
no matter what happens.

1191
01:36:40.628 --> 01:36:42.547
I'm gonna be here for you...

1192
01:36:43.548 --> 01:36:45.049
always.

1193
01:36:48.303 --> 01:36:49.721
I should get some rest now. Mother.

1194
01:37:14.245 --> 01:37:15.872
It's not your fault.

1195
01:37:38.561 --> 01:37:40.938
We all need you. Michael!

1196
01:38:16.599 --> 01:38:19.936
How are you feeling? 
-I'm okay.

1197
01:38:20.019 --> 01:38:22.688
You know. I'm still in a lot of pain.

1198
01:38:23.815 --> 01:38:26.109
But the doctors say I'm healing. 
So...

1199
01:38:26.192 --> 01:38:27.360
Well. that's good news.

1200
01:38:28.277 --> 01:38:29.946
All these kids here...

1201
01:38:31.322 --> 01:38:32.615
They won't fully heal

1202
01:38:32.698 --> 01:38:35.034
and there's burns 
all over their bodies.

1203
01:38:35.785 --> 01:38:37.203
It just breaks my heart.

1204
01:38:38.162 --> 01:38:39.455
It truly does.

1205
01:38:41.958 --> 01:38:43.626
You know. it got me thinking...

1206
01:38:45.420 --> 01:38:47.088
I need to do more for them.

1207
01:38:48.172 --> 01:38:50.383
How much are we getting 
for the accident.

1208
01:38:50.466 --> 01:38:52.343
It should be around seven figures.

1209
01:38:52.969 --> 01:38:55.888
I need every penny donated
to the burn center here.

1210
01:38:57.098 --> 01:38:59.183
Please. you got to make that happen.

1211
01:38:59.267 --> 01:39:00.309
Yeah. of course.

1212
01:39:03.771 --> 01:39:05.481
I'm getting really sleepy.

1213
01:39:07.483 --> 01:39:08.734
These pain meds.

1214
01:39:12.321 --> 01:39:15.366
You get some rest
and I'll come check on you tomorrow.

1215
01:39:16.659 --> 01:39:17.660
Okay.

1216
01:39:20.079 --> 01:39:21.539
Did you bring that?

1217
01:39:21.622 --> 01:39:24.250
Oh. the mouse. yeah. That's from me.

1218
01:39:25.418 --> 01:39:26.961
I love that.
-Good.

1219
01:39:28.212 --> 01:39:29.213
Thank you. Branca.

1220
01:39:29.297 --> 01:39:30.548
I'll see you tomorrow.
-See you.

1221
01:39:32.508 --> 01:39:37.805
If that boy doesn't go on tour.
everything we have falls apart.

1222
01:39:37.889 --> 01:39:41.934
I'm talking deals.
sponsorships. our reputation.

1223
01:39:42.018 --> 01:39:43.728
Everything. Everything just gone.

1224
01:39:43.811 --> 01:39:45.146
Everything here.

1225
01:39:46.606 --> 01:39:48.649
The boys won't 
be able to tour anymore.

1226
01:39:49.275 --> 01:39:50.485
Not without Michael.

1227
01:39:51.110 --> 01:39:53.613
Your son just got out of ICU.

1228
01:39:56.699 --> 01:39:59.368
Michael never wanted to do
The Victory Tour to begin with.

1229
01:39:59.452 --> 01:40:02.079
You planned this entire thing
behind his back.

1230
01:40:13.883 --> 01:40:16.844
When are you gonna realize
he's on his own path?

1231
01:40:19.722 --> 01:40:22.141
And sometimes. you need
to get out of the way.

1232
01:40:25.770 --> 01:40:27.688
Otherwise. you're gonna lose him.

1233
01:40:30.983 --> 01:40:32.610
What about the other boys?

1234
01:40:33.236 --> 01:40:35.530
They'll find their own path.

1235
01:40:51.587 --> 01:40:53.005
You know something. Bill?

1236
01:40:53.589 --> 01:40:56.217
What's that?
-God's been very good to me.

1237
01:40:56.300 --> 01:40:58.135
That he has.

1238
01:40:59.303 --> 01:41:00.805
Not just the accident.

1239
01:41:01.514 --> 01:41:03.933
You know. ... I almost died...

1240
01:41:05.560 --> 01:41:07.311
but I was given a second chance.

1241
01:41:08.354 --> 01:41:09.564
Yeah. well...

1242
01:41:10.606 --> 01:41:12.108
God gave you a gift. son.

1243
01:41:13.526 --> 01:41:14.944
A platform...

1244
01:41:16.028 --> 01:41:17.697
to reach the whole world.

1245
01:41:19.574 --> 01:41:20.992
I can't ignore that.

1246
01:41:23.619 --> 01:41:24.537
No.

1247
01:41:27.707 --> 01:41:29.542
I have to shine my light.

1248
01:41:30.459 --> 01:41:32.712
Spread love and joy.

1249
01:41:34.380 --> 01:41:35.590
To heal.

1250
01:41:40.845 --> 01:41:41.762
Yeah.

1251
01:41:44.682 --> 01:41:46.100
That's my destiny.

1252
01:41:48.311 --> 01:41:49.854
I truly believe that.

1253
01:41:50.438 --> 01:41:53.190
Well. why don't we focus
on getting you healthy first?

1254
01:41:53.274 --> 01:41:55.318
Then we can do all those things
you need to do.

1255
01:41:55.401 --> 01:41:56.485
I'm gonna do the tour.

1256
01:41:57.987 --> 01:41:59.071
Are you sure?

1257
01:41:59.905 --> 01:42:01.115
For my family.

1258
01:42:03.576 --> 01:42:04.702
But then I'm ready. Bill.

1259
01:42:09.874 --> 01:42:11.709
I'm gonna look him 
straight in the eye.

1260
01:42:12.376 --> 01:42:13.919
This is my life.

1261
01:42:17.006 --> 01:42:18.215
My path.

1262
01:42:22.928 --> 01:42:24.013
Mine.

1263
01:42:46.410 --> 01:42:48.245
Okay. let's go out there
and tear that stage up.

1264
01:42:48.329 --> 01:42:49.330
Yeah.

1265
01:42:49.413 --> 01:42:50.748
Give the audience
what they deserve.

1266
01:42:50.831 --> 01:42:52.416
Yeah.
-The best show ever.

1267
01:42:53.542 --> 01:42:55.252
I told you what to think.

1268
01:42:56.921 --> 01:42:58.089
I love you guys.

1269
01:42:58.172 --> 01:42:59.882
You ain't like everyone else.

1270
01:42:59.965 --> 01:43:01.634
You think you're better than me. boy?

1271
01:43:01.717 --> 01:43:03.302
Love you. too. Mike.
-I really do.

1272
01:43:03.386 --> 01:43:04.512
Love you too. Mike.

1273
01:43:05.388 --> 01:43:08.516
Nobody else will understand you
outside this place.

1274
01:43:09.225 --> 01:43:12.853
The Jacksons on three. 
One. two. three...

1275
01:43:12.937 --> 01:43:13.896
Jacksons!

1276
01:43:15.648 --> 01:43:17.817
After I give these boys a rest.

1277
01:43:17.900 --> 01:43:20.945
I'm planning an international tour.
-With Michael?

1278
01:43:21.028 --> 01:43:24.615
Yeah. we're gonna hit
all the big arenas and stadiums.

1279
01:43:24.699 --> 01:43:27.034
This is just the beginning
of The Victory Tour.

1280
01:43:27.118 --> 01:43:30.663
You're adding more shows?
-Yeah. we gonna hit every continent.

1281
01:43:30.746 --> 01:43:33.874
But. first of all. we're going
to Paris. London. Tokyo.

1282
01:43:33.958 --> 01:43:36.502
South Africa. You name it.
we gonna be there.

1283
01:43:36.585 --> 01:43:39.463
This is gonna be the biggest
anyone has ever seen.

1284
01:46:31.260 --> 01:46:32.469
Everybody sing.

1285
01:46:42.897 --> 01:46:44.273
Everybody!

1286
01:48:11.694 --> 01:48:12.903
Good job. everybody.

1287
01:48:13.529 --> 01:48:15.030
Did you see that?

1288
01:48:16.115 --> 01:48:17.408
Did you hear them?

1289
01:48:29.336 --> 01:48:30.671
One more.

1290
01:48:30.754 --> 01:48:32.131
You hear that crowd?

1291
01:48:32.798 --> 01:48:34.216
How you feeling. LA?

1292
01:48:35.801 --> 01:48:37.511
How you doing out there?

1293
01:49:55.798 --> 01:49:57.341
I'd like to say thank you

1294
01:49:58.175 --> 01:50:00.719
for six terrific nights here
at Dodger Stadium.

1295
01:50:01.470 --> 01:50:03.472
Also want to thank the entire band.

1296
01:50:03.555 --> 01:50:05.766
They've been incredible.
And most of all...

1297
01:50:06.892 --> 01:50:08.644
I want to thank my brothers...

1298
01:50:10.854 --> 01:50:12.648
and you fans.

1299
01:50:31.250 --> 01:50:32.876
Bring it down. Bring it down.

1300
01:50:34.503 --> 01:50:36.338
Bring down. the music. Bring it.

1301
01:50:39.007 --> 01:50:40.217
Listen up.

1302
01:50:41.885 --> 01:50:43.095
I'd like to say...

1303
01:50:45.139 --> 01:50:47.266
this is our last and final tour.

1304
01:50:53.063 --> 01:50:54.898
That this is our farewell tour!

1305
01:50:55.899 --> 01:51:00.070
Michael! Michael! Michael!

1306
01:51:00.154 --> 01:51:02.447
You've all been wonderful.
It's been a long 20 years.

1307
01:51:02.531 --> 01:51:04.950
Michael! Michael! Michael!

1308
01:51:08.620 --> 01:51:10.247
And we love you all.

1309
01:51:57.461 --> 01:51:59.463
Good night! I love you!

1310
01:51:59.546 --> 01:52:00.797
We love you!

1311
01:52:20.984 --> 01:52:22.945
We love you. Los Angeles!

1312
01:52:27.741 --> 01:52:29.743
You guys are beautiful!

1313
